1.0.27.name: wordpress/davids-ultra-quicktags
1.0.27.description:
This plugin adds up to four new buttons / links to the WordPress Editor panel. You can select to add a quicktag to easily insert: Amazon item links Amazon product searches custom span class custom div class

The settings pane allows you to enter defaults, as well as your own Amazon associate ID.
